  "detailed_description": "Hoo-Boy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707870/extras/d171b4b573feaa0f28eb554c96ccd2d5.avif?t=1667316985\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><br>Want sweeter?<br><br>Hoo-Boy - A platformer game about the adventures of a candy boy hailing from Candy-Land.<br><br>Jump on platforms, avoid traps, defeat enemies, collect coins and find secrets together with our brave hero in his amazing adventure!<br><br>- 25 Levels.<br>- Enemies and traps.<br>- Customization.<br>- Find easter eggs and portal in Candy-Land.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707870/extras/ffdba235bb8b7fbd359ac8b35de26a20.poster.avif?t=1667316985\" width=128 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707870/extras/ffdba235bb8b7fbd359ac8b35de26a20.webm?t=1667316985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707870/extras/ffdba235bb8b7fbd359ac8b35de26a20.mp4?t=1667316985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
